  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SAVED is an atmospheric first-person horror game set in abandoned houses and grim mansions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore dark rooms and narrow corridors, fight zombies, search for weapons, and use light to survive. Solve puzzles, find keys, and unlock doors to access new parts of the house. Danger lurks behind every door, and silence is deceptive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision has a price.<br>The house is watching. And there may be no escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SAVED is an atmospheric first-person horror game set in abandoned houses and grim mansions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore dark rooms and narrow corridors, fight zombies, search for weapons, and use light to survive. Solve puzzles, find keys, and unlock doors to access new parts of the house. Danger lurks behind every door, and silence is deceptive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision has a price.<br>The house is watching. And there may be no escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.poster.avif?t=1771510541\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.webm?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710040/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.mp4?t=1771510541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
